areer\" title=\"Career\">Career<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ami-modi\/#Controversy\" title=\"Controversy\">Controversy<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ami-modi\/#Facts\" title=\"Facts\">Facts<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"BiographyWiki\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080\">Biography\/Wiki<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Ami Modi is a <strong>47<\/strong> years old woman who was born in <strong>New York, USA<\/strong>. Since a young age, she takes an interest in designing the diamond jewellery. Ami and Nirav Modi studied from the same college, <strong>The Wharton School, USA<\/strong> and knew very well each other. <span class=\"st\">They remained in touch after w<\/span>hen Nirav dropped out of the college for joining his maternal uncle, <strong>Mehul Chinubhai Choksi<\/strong>&#8216;s company\u00a0<strong><span class=\"st\">Gitanjali Gems Ltd.<\/span><\/strong><span class=\"st\"> She later got<\/span> married to <strong>Nirav Modi<\/strong> and became his business partner in his diamond jewellery business.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080\">Physical Appearance<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Ami is approximately <strong>5&#8217;4&#8221;<\/strong> tall and weighs around <strong>50 kg<\/strong>. She has black eyes and hair.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/Ami-Modi-1.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1598\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/Ami-Modi-1.jpg\" alt=\"Ami Modi\" width=\"391\" height=\"588\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/Ami-Modi-1.jpg 391w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/Ami-Modi-1-199x300.jpg 199w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 391px) 100vw, 391px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family_Caste_Boyfriend\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080\">Family, Caste &amp; Boyfriend<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>She belongs to a <strong>Hindu<\/strong> family and got married to businessman <strong>Nirav Modi<\/strong>. The couple has two daughters,\u00a0<strong>Apasha Modi<\/strong> &amp; <strong>Ananya Modi<\/strong>, and a son <strong>Rohin Modi<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_1579\" style=\"width: 420px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/Nirav-Modi-with-Ami-Modi.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1579\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1579\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/Nirav-Modi-with-Ami-Modi.jpg\" alt=\"Ami Modi with Nirav Modi\" width=\"410\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/Nirav-Modi-with-Ami-Modi.jpg 410w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/Nirav-Modi-with-Ami-Modi-246x300.jpg 246w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 410px) 100vw, 410px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-1579\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ami Modi with Nirav Modi<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_1600\" style=\"width: 360px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/Ami-Modi-with-her-husband-and-children.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1600\" class=\"wp-image-1600 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/Ami-Modi-with-her-husband-and-children.jpg\" alt=\"Ami Modi with her husband and children\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/Ami-Modi-with-her-husband-and-children.jpg 350w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/Ami-Modi-with-her-husband-and-children-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/Ami-Modi-with-her-husband-and-children-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/Ami-Modi-with-her-husband-and-children-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-1600\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ami Modi with her husband and children<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080\">Career<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>She did her <strong>Master of Business Administration<\/strong> (MBA) from <strong>The Wharton School, University of Pennsylvania, USA<\/strong>. After completing studies, she joins her husband Nirav Modi&#8217;s diamond jewellery business.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/Ami-Modi-4.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1599\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/Ami-Modi-4.jpg\" alt=\"Ami Modi\" width=\"550\" height=\"376\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/Ami-Modi-4.jpg 550w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/Ami-Modi-4-300x205.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Controversy\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080\">Controversy<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>In February 2018, <strong>Punjab National Bank<\/strong> (PNB) filed a complaint against her husband <strong>Nirav Modi<\/strong> by alleging that he was defrauding the bank of approximately Rs. 11, 400 crores. As per the reports, Ami along with her uncle-in-law <strong>Mehul Choksi<\/strong> and brother-in-law <strong>Nishal Modi<\/strong> have also involved in this case of fraud. The bank claimed that they were fraudulently involved in issuing bank guarantees or Letters of Undertakings (LoU) at the Mid Corporate Branch of the bank in the Brady House of Mumbai. However, she left India along with her children on 4 January 2018 to save herself from the investigation. The Directorate of Enforcement handles this case.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Facts\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080\">Facts<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Apart from taking an interest in designing, she loves to travel, read, and write.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Her net worth is around $1.76 billion.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 0px; line-height: 0px; margin: 0; padding: 0; clear: both;\"><\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ami Modi is the wife of billionaire diamond merchant Nirav Modi. She is an NRI and holds an American Passport. As per the reports, she along with her husband involved in the case of fraudulence in the Punjab National Bank (PNB). Check out Ami Modi Wiki, Height, Weight, Age, Boyfriend, Family, Husband, Children, Biography, Facts &amp; More. Biography\/Wiki Ami Modi is a 47 years old woman who was born in New York, USA. Since a young age, she takes an interest in designing the diamond jewellery. Ami and Nirav Modi studied from the same college, The Wharton School, USA and <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":1596,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[2],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1590"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https: